                        <p><b>HALFTIME: </b>Some interesting statistics from halftime:</p>
<p><ul></p>
<p>	<li><b>Nelson</b>, and not <b>Paulus</b>, leads Duke with six assists.</li></p>
<p>	<li><b>Paulus' </b>assist-to-turnover ratio is 0-to-4.</li></p>
<p>	<li>Duke and Pitt both have 19 rebounds.</li></p>
<p></ul></p>

